<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum und <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>lantschr<ex>eiber,</ex></expan> uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        furbacht etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt, den nehst ir hab bey Tachaw
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        wie sie <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab zu Nappurg etwievil
                                <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>potten</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb sie als hewt ir
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> und gen <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>sölt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu ist uns und in
                            <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> als hewt erst ze wissen worden, daz wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf hewt darczu niht wol
                                <expan>geschik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>mocht<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fl<ex>eisziklich</ex></expan>, daz ir ewch die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lasset befolhen und in beholffen wellet sein,
                        als wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawn. So
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir von der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf
                        morn ze nacht gen <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, die mit ewch furbas von den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> reden sol. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. D<expan>at<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vi</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
